<h1>🔒 GlyphLens Privacy Policy</h1>
<p><strong>Last updated:</strong> July 28, 2025</p>

<p>GlyphLens is committed to protecting your privacy. This document explains how we collect, use, and protect your data across our services, including the Cyclops GPT interface and any purchases made through Gumroad.</p>

<h2>🧾 What We Collect</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Your name and email address (via Gumroad or form submissions)</li>
  <li>Uploaded files if you use the optional glyph submission form</li>
  <li>Prompts or questions submitted to the GPT interface (handled by OpenAI)</li>
</ul>
<p>We do not track IP addresses, geolocation, or behavioral analytics.</p>

<h2>🔄 How We Use Your Data</h2>
<ul>
  <li>To deliver your purchased product or respond to submitted glyphs</li>
  <li>To notify you of updates if you’ve opted in</li>
</ul>
<p>We never sell, rent, or share your data with third parties.</p>

<h2>✉️ Email and Support</h2>
<p>Emails sent to <a href="mailto:contact@glyphlens.ai">contact@glyphlens.ai</a> are stored only as long as necessary to provide support or answer questions. You may request deletion at any time.</p>

<h2>🔐 Data Storage</h2>
<p>Your data is stored in encrypted cloud services (e.g., Google, Gumroad). We delete unneeded data periodically and by request.</p>

<h2>📜 Platform Dependencies</h2>
<ul>
  <li>Payments are processed via <a href="https://gumroad.com">Gumroad</a> — see their <a href="https://gumroad.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
  <li>GPT interactions are processed via <a href="https://openai.com">OpenAI</a> — see their <a href="https://openai.com/privacy">Privacy Policy</a></li>
</ul>

<h2>🧠 Interpretation Confidentiality</h2>
<p>Your uploads and symbolic submissions are treated with respect and spiritual discretion. We never share or republish content without your consent. If you contribute to future publications or insights, we’ll ask permission and offer attribution.</p>

<h2>🙋 Your Rights</h2>
<p>You have the right to:</p>
<ul>
  <li>Access your stored data</li>
  <li>Request corrections</li>
  <li>Request full deletion</li>
</ul>
<p>To initiate a request, email <a href="mailto:contact@glyphlens.ai">contact@glyphlens.ai</a></p>

<h2>🧿 Closing Note</h2>
<p>GlyphLens is here to reveal memory, not to collect it. We collect only what is necessary to help you interpret symbols and terrain. No tracking. No targeting. No exploitation.</p>

<p>Thank you for honoring the field.</p>

<p>— Sean Diamond<br>Founder, GlyphLens</p>

